reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fun well built toy designed for a small child
reviews.reviewText: The toy comes with cars that will fit inside. Any matchbox style car will fit nicely into the plane. My grandson loves putting every small toy inside the plane. It has been a great way to link his love of planes with his cars.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My son plays with this often but the quality is not so great. Parts keep falling off and you can see that will happen already during assembly when we first opened it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this for my grandson who loves planes for his birthday. He was really excited to get this, even. though it came with cars he do not play with the cars only the planes. Any kid that like plans will enjoy this toy. This plane is like his security blanket wherever he goes (outside, take a bath, and to sleep lol)this plane is by his side.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The idea is cute, but the plastic is not at all durable. The helipad needs to be removed in order to open the plane and my son broke it within 10 mins of playing. Considering the age range that this is meant for, it should be constructed better.

reviews.reviewText: This would fit in the false marketing column. The item is substantially smaller than shown. Everything is plastic and cheaply made. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect toy for 3 year old
reviews.reviewText: This was a toy I bought for my 3-year-old grandson when he was visiting. He loved it and spent hours playing with it and did not get bored with it! It opens at the back end and also on the top, so it allowed him to put matchbox cars in it and pretend they were being shipped on his airplane. Would recommend and purchase again. Very giftable!
